2011年，萊威在{{link-en|BuddyTV|BuddyTV}}的「2011年電視最性感男人」上排名第九十七位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.buddytv.com/slideshows/white-collar/tvs-100-sexiest-men-of-2011-29104.aspx|title=TV's 100 Sexiest Men of 2011|publisher=[[BuddyTV|BuddyTV]]|accessdate=2012-01-13|archive-date=2018-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180422101322/http://www.buddytv.com/slideshows/white-collar/tvs-100-sexiest-men-of-2011-29104.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他後來放棄出演了Fox電視試播《Let It Go》的男主角，而該劇後來也未執行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2012/02/13/zachary-levi-let-it-go/|title=Pilot Scoop: Zach Levi to Headline Fox's Let It Go|publisher=TvLine|accessdate=2012-02-13|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003924/https://tvline.com/2012/02/13/zachary-levi-let-it-go/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。萊威原本會在[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威電影宇宙]]電影《[[雷神索爾_(電影)|雷神索爾]]》（2011年）中飾演{{link-en|范達爾|Fandral}}一角，但因與《宅男特務》的安排衝突而不得不退出；該角後改由[[約書亞·達拉斯|約書亞·達拉斯]]飾演<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.huffingtonpost.com/mobileweb/2012/06/09/thor-2-zachary-levi-fandral-josh-dallas_n_1583137.html|title='Thor 2': Zachary Levi Eyed For Fandral, Josh Dallas Out Of Film|work=[[huffingtonpost|huffingtonpost]]|date=2012-06-06|accessdate=2012-10-03}}</ref>。萊威在《雷神索爾》的續集《[[雷神索爾2：黑暗世界|雷神索爾2：黑暗世界]]》（2013年）中取代達拉斯飾演范達爾，因達拉斯有著自己行程上的安排衝突；之後，他也在下一步續集《[[雷神索爾3：諸神黃昏|雷神索爾3：諸神黃昏]]》（2017年）中飾演同角。2013年8月，萊威出演了[[百老匯|百老匯]]音樂喜劇《{{link-en|第一次約會 (音樂劇)|First Date (musical)|第一次約會}}》<ref>{{cite news|last=Carlson|first=Adam|title=Zachary Levi made his Broadway debut in 'First Date'|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/05/20/zachary-levi-broadway-first-date/|accessdate=2013-08-19|newspaper=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-05-20|archive-date=2014-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329064858/http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/05/20/zachary-levi-broadway-first-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年1月，宣布，萊威將於NBC電視劇《[[超異能英雄再啟|超異能英雄再啟]]》中主演13集<ref>{{cite news|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|title=Zachary Levi to Lead ''Heroes Reborn'' Miniseries on NBC|url=http://tvline.com/2015/01/16/zachary-levi-heroes-reborn-cast-nbc/|accessdate=2015-01-16|website=[[TVLine|TVLine]]|date=2015-01-16|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123023351/https://tvline.com/2015/01/16/zachary-levi-heroes-reborn-cast-nbc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但該劇並未獲得第二季的續訂<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/01/13/heroes-reborn-canceled-as-nbc-plays-the-limited-series-card/|title=‘Heroes Reborn’ canceled as NBC plays the ‘limited series’ card|website=TV By The Numbers by zap2it.com|access-date=2016-04-22|archive-date=2016-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116012323/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2016/01/13/heroes-reborn-canceled-as-nbc-plays-the-limited-series-card/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2015年6月，萊威被證實於電視動畫《{{link-en|魔髮奇緣 (電視劇)|Tangled: The Series|魔髮奇緣}}》中再度為費林·雷德／尤金·費茲伯特配音，並於2017年推出<ref name="TangledTV">{{cite news|last=Bryant|first=Jacob|title='Tangled' Animated TV Series Based on Film Coming to Disney Channel|url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/tangled-ever-after-jeffrey-tambor-jonathan-banks-george-eads-macgyver-1201724520/|work=Variety|date=2016-03-08|accessdate=2016-04-10|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803115451/https://variety.com/2016/tv/news/tangled-ever-after-jeffrey-tambor-jonathan-banks-george-eads-macgyver-1201724520/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

後來，萊威加入了百老匯音樂劇《{{link-en|她愛我|She Loves Me}}》的演出，並飾演主角喬治·諾瓦克。它於2016年3月17日在[[54俱樂部|54俱樂部]]首演、於2016年2月19日進行預演，並於6月12日前進行了有限的表演<ref>Cox, Gordon. [http://variety.com/2015/legit/news/zachary-levi-broadway-she-loves-me-1201582742/ "Zachary Levi to Star in Broadway's 'She Loves Me'] {{Wayback|url=http://variety.com/2015/legit/news/zachary-levi-broadway-she-loves-me-1201582742/ |date=20200821013655 }} Variety.com, 2015-09-01.</ref><ref name=datechanges>{{cite web|url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/182547/broadways-she-loves-me-starring-laura-benanti-zachary-levi-more-sets-new-dates/|title=Broadway's She Loves Me, Starring Laura Benanti, Zachary Levi & More, Sets New Dates|publisher=broadway.com|access-date=2017-10-31|archive-date=2020-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200510193317/https://www.broadway.com/buzz/182547/broadways-she-loves-me-starring-laura-benanti-zachary-levi-more-sets-new-dates/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來，該劇延續至7月10日<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/article/she-loves-me-announces-broadway-extension|title=She Loves Me Announces Broadway Extension  {{!}} Playbill|website=Playbill|access-date=2016-04-22|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023224824/https://www.playbill.com/article/she-loves-me-announces-broadway-extension|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/article/she-loves-me-closes-on-broadway-tonight|title=She Loves Me Closes on Broadway Today  {{!}} Playbill|website=Playbill|access-date=2016-07-12|archive-date=2016-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160713214007/http://www.playbill.com/article/she-loves-me-closes-on-broadway-tonight|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《她愛我》獲得了評論家高度的讚賞，除了得到《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的認可外，還在《[[衛報|衛報]]》贏得了五顆星的高評<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/stage/2016/mar/18/she-loves-me-musical-broadway-review|title=She Loves Me review – a show to fall head over heels for|last=Soloski|first=Alexis|date=2016-03-18|newspaper=The Guardian|issn=0261-3077|access-date=2016-04-22|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924113657/https://www.theguardian.com/stage/2016/mar/18/she-loves-me-musical-broadway-review|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/18/theater/review-she-loves-me-is-a-daydream-of-the-ordinary.html|title=Review: ‘She Loves Me’ Is a Daydream of the Ordinary|last=Brantley|first=Ben|date=2016-03-17|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-04-22|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301004558/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/18/theater/review-she-loves-me-is-a-daydream-of-the-ordinary.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。萊威也為此入圍了[[東尼獎最佳音樂劇男主角|東尼獎最佳音樂劇男主角]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tonyawards.com/en_US/nominees/shows/201511091447111422562.html|title=The Tony Award Nominees - Shows|website=TonyAwards.com|access-date=2016-05-23|archive-date=2018-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221041715/https://www.tonyawards.com/en_US/nominees/shows/201511091447111422562.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。評論家稱讚了他對喬治的詮釋，認為他「有時瀟灑、帥氣、對他人無禮」，且「散發著一點點甜美的謙虛。」<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.timeout.com/newyork/theater/she-loves-me|title=She Loves Me|website=Time Out New York|access-date=2016-04-22|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124005550/https://www.timeout.com/newyork/theater/she-loves-me|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/laura-benanti-zachary-levi-she-875850|title=Laura Benanti, Zachary Levi in 'She Loves Me': Theater Review|website=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=2016-04-22|archive-date=2020-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200510193351/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/laura-benanti-zachary-levi-she-875850|dead-url=no}}</ref>

