== 個人生活 ==
萊威是一名[[跑車|跑車]]和[[摩托車|摩托車]]的愛好者，並擁有一輛2009年的[[日產GT-R|日產GT-R]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.adamcarolla.com/CarCastBlog/2010/07/16/zach-levi |title=Zach Levi |last=Carolla |first=Adam |date=2010-07-16 |work=[[CarCast|CarCast]] |accessdate=2010-09-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100923205046/http://www.adamcarolla.com/CarCastBlog/2010/07/16/zach-levi |archivedate=2010-09-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last=Nygaard |first=Sandra |date=2007-10 |title=With a name like Levi, he's gotta know jeans |work=Men's Health |volume=22 |issue=8 |page=134}}</ref>。他也喜歡玩電子遊戲，如《[[超級瑪利歐兄弟|超級瑪利歐兄弟]]》。萊威信奉於[[基督教|基督教]]。

2010年9月，萊威創立了自己的公司The Nerd Machine<ref>{{cite news|title=Zac Launches The Nerd Machine|work=ChuckTV.net|url=http://chucktv.net/2010/09/24/zac-launches-the-nerd-machine|accessdate=2010-09-24|archive-date=2012-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120201184444/http://chucktv.net/2010/09/24/zac-launches-the-nerd-machine/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他曾被選為[[2011年NBA全明星賽|2011年NBA全明星賽]]的名人全明星賽參賽者；當時，他待在[[魔術強森|魔術強森]]打球<ref>{{cite news|first=Rich|last=Sands|title=Justin Bieber, Ty Burrell and Zachary Levi Hoop It Up for NBA All-Star Celebrity Game|url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/Justin-Bieber-Ty-1028767.aspx|accessdate=2012-10-03|newspaper=[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]]|date=2011-02-01|archive-date=2014-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419130340/http://www.tvguide.com/news/justin-bieber-ty-1028767.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年6月16日，加拿大女演員{{link-en|梅西·帕瑞格蘭|Missy Peregrym}}宣布，她已和萊威於[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]][[茂宜島|茂宜島]]結婚<ref name="marriage">{{cite web |last=Marquina |first=Sierra |url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/zachary-levi-secretly-marries-girlfriend-missy-peregrym-in-maui-pic-2014166 |title=Zachary Levi Secretly Marries Girlfriend Missy Peregrym In Maui: Pic – Us Weekly |publisher=Usmagazine.com |accessdate=2014-06-17 |archive-date=2018-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629155147/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/zachary-levi-secretly-marries-girlfriend-missy-peregrym-in-maui-pic-2014166/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他們於2015年4月提出離婚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/article/zachary-levi-missy-peregrym-divorce|title=Zachary Levi and Missy Peregrym Are Divorcing|date=2015-04-20|publisher=People|access-date=2017-10-30|archive-date=2016-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531113250/http://www.people.com/article/zachary-levi-missy-peregrym-divorce|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其離婚的法庭文件日期記為2014年12月3日<ref name="divorce">{{cite web |url=http://www.tmz.com/2015/04/18/zachary-levi-missy-peregrym-divorce-secretly-married/ |title=Zachary Levi & Missy Peregrym Secret Wedding Ends In Even More Secret Divorce |publisher=TMZ.com |date= |accessdate=2015-04-18 |archive-date=2020-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216013722/https://www.tmz.com/2015/04/18/zachary-levi-missy-peregrym-divorce-secretly-married/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

